attributes.Long form description: The student has to change the battery of the Gopro. He has a hard time finding the battery door, but the teacher gives him directions to find it quickly so he can change the battery. Then he has to replace the SD card with a new one. Next the student has to turn on the Gopro, but he makes a mistake and presses the record button, so he has to stop recording so he can press the power button and then press it again to turn the Gopro off.  The student then places the strap on the Gopro.He then has to switch the Gopro from the strap to the handheld grip, to finally remove the handheld grip from the Gopro.
